<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>救生艇新闻：博客——保护人类</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 13:00:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>血液测试可以在症状或脑部扫描发生变化前数年预测阿尔茨海默病的进展</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/blood-test-can-predict-alzheimers-disease-progression-years-before-symptoms-or-brain-scan-changes</link><description>麻省总医院布里格姆分校的研究人员进行的一项研究发现，对阿尔茨海默病生物标志物——血浆磷酸化 tau 217 (pTau217) 进行血液检测，可以预测认知健康老年人淀粉样蛋白 PET 扫描变化的进展情况和认知能力下降。这些发现可能有助于推迟时间，实现更简单、更早的疾病预测，并表明谁可能面临认知能力下降的风险。结果发表于&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/blood-test-can-predict-alzheimers-disease-progression-years-before-symptoms-or-brain-scan-changes.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 13:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/blood-test-can-predict-alzheimers-disease-progression-years-before-symptoms-or-brain-scan-changes</guid></item><item><title>人工智能模型可以帮助减少透析患者的住院时间</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ai-model-can-help-cut-hospitalizations-in-patients-with-dialysis</link><description>AI 模型识别出接受血液透析的终末期肾病 (ESKD) 患者，这些患者因感染或体液状态异常而面临着入院的迫在眉睫的风险。当与护士主导的病例审查和有针对性的干预措施相结合时，该策略有助于避免短期入院，展示了人工智能指导及时、有针对性的护理的潜力。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/ai-model-can-help-cut-hospitalizations-in-patients-with-dialysis.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 12:45:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/ai-model-can-help-cut-hospitalizations-in-patients-with-dialysis</guid></item><item><title>大脑回路之间的竞争是智能行为的关键</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/competition-between-brain-circuits-is-key-to-intelligent-behavior</link><description>大脑不仅进行合作，而且进行合作。它也竞争。牛津大学、剑桥大学、庞培法布拉大学和加拿大蒙特利尔神经学研究所联合发表在《自然神经科学》杂志上的一项国际研究得出了这样的结论。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/competition-between-brain-circuits-is-key-to-intelligent-behavior2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 12:30:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/competition-between-brain-circuits-is-key-to-intelligent-behavior</guid></item><item><title>听力研究追踪关键内耳蛋白质的进化</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/hearing-research-traces-evolution-of-key-inner-ear-protein-2</link><description>TMC1 如何进化来感知声音的发现可以指导未来的听力损失治疗&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/hearing-research-traces-evolution-of-key-inner-ear-protein2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 12:15:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/hearing-research-traces-evolution-of-key-inner-ear-protein-2</guid></item><item><title>兄弟姐妹干细胞移植使“奥斯陆患者”的艾滋病毒罕见缓解</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/sibling-stem-cell-transplant-leads-to-rare-hiv-remission-in-oslo-patient</link><description>收到后&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/sibling-stem-cell-transplant-leads-to-rare-hiv-remission-in-oslo-patient.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 12:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/sibling-stem-cell-transplant-leads-to-rare-hiv-remission-in-oslo-patient</guid></item><item><title>COVID-19 感染后肌钙蛋白升高的蛋白质组学见解</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/proteomic-insights-into-troponin-elevation-following-covid-19-infection</link><description>背景&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/proteomic-insights-into-troponin-elevation-following-covid-19-infection2.jpg" /&gt;由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 14 Apr 2026 11:45:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/proteomic-insights-into-troponin-elevation-following-covid-19-infection</guid></item><item><title>围产期 HIV 暴露和 HIV 疾病严重程度与青少年血压的关系</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/04/association